    <abstract id="aspace_89297266811fd11933606a3563b48f94" label="Abstract">Peter Gregg was a Pittsburgh area actor and playwright.  This collection includes his play scripts, correspondence, memorabilia, employment records, book reviews, and photographs.</abstract>
